== Chatlino

Chatlino is a one simple application that provides just
online-chatting functionality.

== Requriements

* ruby-openid
* openid

== Run Chatlino with Juggernaut as push solution

* Confirmed that PUSH_SOLUTION is set to "juggernaut" in environment.rb

* Created your own config/juggernaut_config.yml based on
  config/juggernaut_config.yml.template

* Run juggernaut -c config/juggernaut.yml

* Run this rails app in anyway you prefer

